BonnieCMS is a minimalist CMS suitable for small and medium-sized sites.
This cms does not use any type of traditional database, the data is stored through a database that works with flat files.

The fact that it is minimalist, not to say that it is also in the number of features implemented.
BonnieCMS is minimal because its architecture has been designed to be as simple as possible.

He is currently in full development and version will be enriched with many new features, so there will be some time before it becomes really stable.

BonnieCMS is totally free, and is released under the MIT license.

Features

- on a flat file database
- template system
- extensible through plugins
- multilanguage support
- minimum installation requirements (only PHP> = 5.1)
